| -------------- | ---------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Tenant         | AWS Organization | Organization                       |
| Subscription   | AWS Account      | Project                            |
| Resource Group | N/A              | (Project itself acts as container) |
| VNet           | VPC              | VPC                                |
| NSG            | Security Group   | Firewall Rule                      |
| NAT Gateway    | NAT Gateway      | Cloud NAT                          |
